  "markup": "\u003Cp style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;\u0022 class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022\u003E\u003Cspan style=\u0022mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-ligatures: none;\u0022\u003EWe are committed to providing a smoke-free and vape-free work environment to promote the health, safety, and comfort of all of you, clients, and visitors. Smoking and vaping are prohibited in all indoor company facilities, company vehicles, and within a designated distance from building entrances, windows, and ventilation systems. You are expected to adhere to this policy and use designated outdoor areas, if available, for smoking or vaping.\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp style=\u0022mso-margin-top-alt: auto; mso-margin-bottom-alt: auto;\u0022 class=\u0022MsoNormal\u0022\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E"
